data.description: H12942 - The admired and popular “Almanor” model is move-in ready & a MUST SEE! The only Single-Family home in Maple Ridge with 12ft ceilings that is currently listed under 480K! This lovely corner lot home has been recently painted, power washed (exterior including the roof), and is vacant for a quick closing. Kitchen upgrades include 42” cabinets, newer stainless-steel appliances, a pantry, granite countertops, and tons of cabinet storage and counter space. Additional upgrades include tile throughout, extended exterior front entry pavers, TV wall mount cable ready in the living room, and a spacious patio that is ready for a pool. The master bedroom has a large soaking tub, dual sinks, a large shower, elevated sinks for your convenience, and an expansive closet with plenty of space to add storage. The Master bedroom door to the lanai is impact glass. The home includes window treatments throughout and cabinets in the laundry room for extra storage. Excellent location that is within walking distance of the clubhouse and mailboxes. Schedule a showing today.
